summary: Morgan Stanley notes that last night, President Trump posted on social media an announcement of 100% tariffs on all movies coming into the U.S. produced in “Foreign Lands.” In the bear case, this likely reduces the earnings power of all companies in the value chain, the firm says, adding that 100% tariffs on some or all of the cost of a film would lead to fewer films, more expensive films, and lower earnings for all in the business.
